icult.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20got%20hundreds%20of%20drone%20makers%20all%20over%20the%20place%20building%20all%20kinds%20of%20drones%2C%20giving%20Ukraine%20a%20chaotic%20arsenal%20resembling%20a%20spilled%20toolbox.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20this%20can%20create%20challenges%20for%20Ukraine's%20drone%20pilots%2C%20it%20also%20has%20some%20real%20advantages%20as%20the%20country%20fights%20back%20against%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-did-russia-invade-ukraine-putin-politics-motive-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERussia's%20invasion%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-says-world-largest-producer-tactical-strategic-drones-war-russia-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUkraine%20makes%20most%20of%20its%20drones%3C%2Fa%3E%20itself%2C%20something%20of%20critical%20importance%20considering%20the%20dominant%20role%20drones%20play%20in%20the%20conflict%20and%20the%20unpredictability%20of%20Western%20aid%2C%20particularly%20US%20security%20assistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20said%20more%20than%2096%25%20of%20the%201.5%20million%20drones%20it%20bought%20last%20year%20were%20of%20Ukrainian%20origin%2C%20coming%20from%20countless%20outfits%2C%20some%20from%20workshops%2C%20garages%2C%20and%20basements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20in%20combat%20dress%20and%20with%20facial%20hair%20holds%20a%20small%20drone%20behind%20a%20table%20with%20a%20laptop%20and%20in%20front%20of%20a%20Ukrainian%20flag%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67daac18585f1dff88b28d8c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221331%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20military%20engineer%20programs%20Ukrainian%20FPV%20drones%20%26quot%3BGeneral%20Chereshnya%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Zaporizhzhia%20sector%2C%20southeastern%20Ukraine.%3Cp%3EDmytro%20Smolienko%20%2F%20Ukrinform%2FFuture%20Publishing%20via%20Get