ast%2C%20Russia%20has%20fewer%20types%2C%20and%20that%20makes%20it%20easier%20to%20identify%20and%20learn%20how%20to%20defeat%20them.%20The%20result%20for%20Ukraine%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20%26quot%3Bit's%20very%20easy%20for%20us%20to%20surprise%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20men%20work%20on%20drone%20components%20over%20a%20wooden%20table%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67daad3c69253ccddf99a963%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221334%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMen%20work%20at%20a%20factory%20producing%20drones%20for%20the%20Ukrainian%20Armed%20Forces%20in%20Kyiv%2C%20Ukraine.%3Cp%3EVitalii%20Nosach%2FGlobal%20Images%20Ukraine%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20because%20Russia%20is%20often%20slower%20to%20innovate%2C%20it%20makes%20it%20easier%20for%20Ukraine%20to%20learn%20how%20to%20disrupt%20Russia's%20drones%20with%20electronic%20warfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJames%20Patton%20Rogers%2C%20a%20drone%20expert%20at%20the%20Cornell%20Brooks%20Tech%20Policy%20Institute%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20it%20would%20work%20in%20Russia's%20favor%20for%20the%20Ukrainians%20to%20use%20only%20a%20few%20drone%20types.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20fewer%20drones%20to%20worry%20about%2C%20it%20could%20%26quot%3Bfix%20onto%20one%20type%20of%20drone%2C%20find%20out%20what%20its%20signal%20is%2C%20what%20its%20counter%20electronic%20warfare%20measures%20are%2C%20what%20it%20does%20to%20protect%20itself%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20jam%20it%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20have%20all%20of%20these%20different%20drones%20and%20they're%20built%20by%20different%20manufacturers%20and%20they're%20super%20high-tech%2C%20well%2C%20you%20have%20an%20advantage%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20explaining%20that%20is%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20it%20becomes%20harder%20for%20your%20enemy%20to%20then%20identify%26quot%3B%20a%20way%20to%20take%20the%