%20government%20decades%20ago%20to%20prevent%20a%20demographic%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirstly%2C%20I%20think%20the%20biggest%20challenge%20is%20the%20whole%20intent%20of%20family%20planning%20which%20was%20prescribed%20by%20the%20government%20of%20India%20in%20late%2070s%20and%2080s%20was%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20country%20doesn't%20suffer%20from%20a%20demographic%20challenge.%20So%2C%20those%20states%20that%20have%20done%20exceptionally%20well%20in%20population%20control%20today%2C%20if%20you%20go%20back%20in%20time%20and%20start%20penalising%20them%2C%20then%20that's%20certainly%20a%20travesty%20of%20justice%2C%26quot%3B%20KTR%20told%20NDTV%20today%20after%20a%20meeting%20on%20the%20delimitation%20exercise%20held%20in%20Chennai%20got%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Telangana%20MLA%20cautioned%20that%20after%20a%20population-based%20delimitation%2C%20three-four%20states%20could%20end%20up%20determining%20the%20political%20roadmap%20for%20the%20whole%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20states%20that%20have%20had%20explosive%20population%20growth%20despite%20the%20government%20of%20India's%20prescription%2C%20today%20cannot%20be%20asked%20to%20run%20the%20country%20and%20decide%20the%20future%20course%20of%20action%20for%20the%20country.%20What%20we%20are%20proposing%20is%20a%20fair%20delimitation%2C%26quot%3B%20KTR%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we%20are%20proposing%20is%20a%20consultative%20approach.%20What%20we%20are%20proposing%20and%20requesting%20is%20that%20the%20government%20of%20India%20does%20not%20act%20in%20a%20unilateral%20fashion.%20Instead%2C%20go%20in%20a%20consultative%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20had%20assured%20southern%20states%20that%20they%20won't%20lose%20even%20a%20single%20seat%2C%20rather%20they%20will%20gain%20seats%20on%20a%20pro-rata%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKTR%2C%20however%2C%20expressed%20doubt%20over%20Mr%20Shah's%20assurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSouthern%20states%20do%20not%20lose%20%5Bseats%5D%20does%20not%20mean%20that%20northern%20states%20will%20not%20gain%20disproportionately.%20That's%20the%20concern%2C%20that%20the%20south%20may%20nominally%20see%20an%20increase%20in%20seats%2C%20but%20the%20north%20may%20get%20a%20disproportionate%20%5Bnumber%20of%20seats%5D%2C%26quot%3B%20KTR%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20it%20may%20not%20be%20accurate%20to%20say%20all%20southern%20states%20are%20coming%20together%20and%20opposing%20the%20delimitation%20exercise%20in%20its%20current%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWell%2C%20I%20think%20it's%20an%20issue-based%20thing.%20You%20know%2C%20we%20are%20Indians%20first%2C%20then%20we%20are%20south%20Indians%2C%20then%20we%20are%20Telangana%2C%20then%20Telugu%2C%20etc.%20Punjab%20and%20Odisha%20joined%20us%20and%20West%20Bengal%20is%20also%20likely%20to%20join%20us%20%5Bon%20the%20delimitation%20debate%5D%2C%26quot%3B%20KTR%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20suppose%20it's%20just%20a%20good%20beginning%20on%20a%20very%20good%20issue.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20joint%20action%20committee%20(JAC)%20on%20delimitation%20at%20the%20meeting%20today%20unanimously%20adopted%20a%20resolution%20that%20said%20any%20delimitation%20exercise%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20Centre%20should%20be%20done%20transparently%20and%20after%20discussion%20and%20deliberation%20with%20all%20stakeholders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JAC%20on%20delimitation%20was%20held%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin.%20Leaders%20who%20attended%20include%20Kerala%20Chief%20Minister%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan%2C%20Telangana%20Chief%20Minister%20Revanth%20Reddy%2C%20Punjab%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhagwant%20Mann%2C%20Karnataka%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20DK%20Shivakumar%2C%20Odisha%20Congress%20president%20Bhakta%20Charan%20Das%2C%20and%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20leader%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20Das%20Burma%2C%20among%20others.%20Form