0into%20a%20giant%20beauty%20chain%20over%20its%2055-year%20history.%20Here's%20how%20Sephora%20became%20so%20successful.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jmcgrath%40insider.com%20(Jenny%20McGrath)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsephora-history%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20import%20steel%20parts%20from%20China.%20Trump's%20tariffs%20won't%20stop%20me%20%26amp%3Bmdash%3B%20it's%20still%20cheaper%20and%20easier.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side%20by%20side%20composite%20image%20showing%2C%20left%2C%20Moneta%20Mart's%20point-of-sale%20unit%2C%20and%20right%2C%20Moneta%20Mart%20CEO%20Michael%20King.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67dd514263d72727e197de38%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELeft%2C%20Moneta%20Market's%20point-of-sale%20unit%2C%20and%20right%2C%20Moneta%20Mart%20CEO%20Michael%20King.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Michael%20King%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMike%20King%20runs%20a%20micro-market%20business%20for%20which%20he%20sources%20steel%20components%20from%20China.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20says%20that%20Trump's%20steel%20tariffs%20don't%20make%20sourcing%20in%20the%20US%20more%20attractive%20for%20him.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20believes%20it's%20still%20cheaper%20%E2%80%94%20and%20much%20easier%20%E2%80%94%20to%20source%20from%20China.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Mike%20King%2C%20who%20runs%20a%20suite%20of%20vending%20machines%20as%20well%20as%20Moneta%20Market%2C%20a%20full-service%20micro-market%20company%20based%20in%20Salt%20Lake%20City.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20out%20with%20gumball%20machines.%20I%20was%20in%20college%20serving%20tables%2C%20when%20I%20read%20an%20e-book%20online%2C%20and%20started%20buying%20them%20for%20about%20%2450%20a%20pop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20I%20met%20a%20guy%20who%20was%20selling%20full-size%20snack%20and%20soda%20machines%20and%20he%20was%20kind%20of%20laughing%20at%20me%3A%20%26quot%3BWhy%20are%20you%20messing%20around%20with%20all%20that%20small%20money%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20going%20to%20do%20it%2C%20do%20it%20for%20real.%26quot%3B%20So%20I%20decided%20to%20go%20all%20in%20on%20vending%2C%20and%20built%20that%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20I%20learned%20how%20to%20do%20micro-markets%2C%20and%20realized%20the%20profit%20was%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20micro-market%20is%20a%20small%2C%20unstaffed%20shop%20where%20people%20can%20just%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Egrab%20things%2C%20pay%2C%20and%20go.%20Our%20point-of-sale%20systems%20are%20housed%20in%20steel%20boxes%20that%20we%20manufacture%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20run%20about%20350%20of%20them%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fdcc5ea2-d568-4568-9ecc-6e5488d7f88c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20not%20realistic%20for%20me%20to%20buy%20them%20in%20the%20US%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFour%20years%20ago%2C%20when%20we%20started%20making%20these%20boxes%2C%20my%20initial%20impulse%20was%20to%20see%20if%20we%20can%20make%20them%20down%20the%20road%2C%20or%20in%20manufacturing%20hubs%20like%20Detroit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverwhelmingly%2C%20it%20was%20difficult%20to%20communicate%20with%20and%20deal%20with%20any%20American%20company%20that%20we%20reached%20out%20to.%20So%20I%20went%20with%20Chinese%20manufacturers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%20and%20March%2C%20Trump%20announced%20that%20the%20US%20was%20implementing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-25-tariffs-steel-aluminum-imports-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E25%25%20tariffs%20on%20any%20steel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20plus%20a%20total%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-trade-war-china-prices-electronics-appliances-apparel-cars-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E20%25%20on%20anything%20from%20China%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20already%20had%20a%2025%25%20tariff%20on%20Chinese%20steel%2C%20so%20I'm%20sitting%20there%20thinking%2C%20%26quot%3BWell%2C%20does%20that%20mean%20I%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ecould%20have%20a%2070%25%20tariff%20if%20I%20order%20steel%20from%20China%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20doing%20the%20math.%20To%20actually%20deter%20me%20from%20ordering%20from%20China%20at%20this%20point%2C%20the%20tariffs%20would%20still%20have%20to%20be%20quite%20a%20lot%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20buying%20my%20boxes%20at%20about%20%24250%2C%20and%20a%2070%25%20tariff%20would%20add%20another%20%24175%2C%20making%20them%20%24425.%20Once%20it's%20shipped%20and%20through%20customs%2C%20it'd%20be%20about%20%24825%20per%20box.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20I%20might%20be%20able%20to%20do%20all%20that%20for%20%241%2C000-%241%2C200.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20the%20price%20in%20China%20got%20to%20be%20a%20few%20hundred%20dollars%20more%2C%20I'm%20probably%20still%20ordering%20from%20China%2C%20just%20because%20it's%20so%20much%20easier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f7fbe7e6-67a4-43cb-bec8-50990a692585%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EChina%20just%20geared%20up%20better%20for%20this%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20that%20once%20China%20realized%20that%20they%20were%20going%20to%20be%20the%20manufacturer%20for%20the%20world%2C%20they%20embraced%20that%20wholeheartedly%20and%20built%20an%20entire%20infrastructure%20around%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20just%20don't%20see%20how%20America%20can%20compete%20at%20all%20with%20what%20China%20has%20built.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20box%20needs%20to%20be%20powder%20coated%2C%20and%20that%20also%20needs%20custom%20foam%20packaging%20around%20it%2C%20and%20a%20custom%20box%20made%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20send%20a%20job%20to%20a%20metal%20factory%2C%20they're%20making%20the%20box%20and%20then%20they're%20putting%20it%20on%20a%20truck%20and%20shipping%20it%20down%20the%20road%20to%20a%20place%20that's%20powder-coating%20it.%20Then%20they're%20sending%20to%20a%20place%20making%20custom%20Styrofoam%20boxes%2C%20and%20then%20shipping%20it%20to%20a%20place%20with%20cardboard%20boxes%20made%20that%20fit%20perfectly.%20Then%20someone's%20shipping%20it%20down%20to%20the%20boat%20yard%20to%20get%20it%20to%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20those%20logistics%20are%20part%20of%20the%20price%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20think%20about%20any%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20might%20find%20a%20place%20in%20Fresno%20that's%20willing%20to%20make%20my%20metal%20boxes%20for%20a%20reasonable%20price%2C%20but%20there%20are%20so%20many%20more%20headaches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20China%2C%20when%20they%20encountered%20a%20design%20issue%2C%20they%20scratched%20their%20heads%20for%20a%20bit%20%E2%80%94%20and%20within%20a%20week%2C%20had%20proposed%20tweaks.%20When%20companies%20in%20the%20US%20saw%20my%20designs%2C%20they%20threw%20up%20so%20many%20roadblocks%20and%20would%20have%20charged%20so%20much%20more%20to%20adapt%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20US%20maker%20is%20also%20likely%20not%20going%20to%20powder%20coat%20the%20boxes%2C%20or%20package%20them%2C%20so%20that%20becomes%20my%20job%20to%20organize.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20the%20tariffs%20will%20likely%20just%20add%20some%20costs%20to%20my%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20a%20logistical%20nightmare%20to%20try%20to%20get%20something%20like%20what%20I'm%20trying%20to%20do%20done%20in%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbusiness-buys-steel-parts-china-trump-tariffs-wont-change-easier-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742639462000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67dd514463d72727e