esy%20of%20Kevin%20Hart%20and%20Mike%20Gorius%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMike%20Gorius%20and%20Kevin%20Hart%20opt%20for%20private%20lenders%20despite%20higher%20interest%20rates.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20main%20advantage%20of%20working%20with%20private%20lenders%20rather%20than%20traditional%20lenders%20is%20speed.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFinding%20people%20with%20capital%20boils%20down%20to%20networking%2C%20leveraging%20social%20media%2C%20and%20cold-calling.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20of%20March%202025%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftodays-mortgage-rates-thursday-20-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emortgage%20rates%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20are%20hovering%20around%206.4%25.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReal-estate%20investors%20Mike%20Gorius%20and%20Kevin%20Hart%20are%20willing%20to%20pay%20nearly%20double%20that%20rate%20to%20work%20with%20private%20money%20lenders.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20main%20reason%20is%20speed%20and%20efficiency.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGorius%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20compared%20to%20working%20with%20a%20traditional%20lender%2C%20%26quot%3Bthere's%20a%20lot%20less%20paperwork%20and%20a%20lot%20fewer%20hoops%20to%20jump%20through.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20and%20Hart%2C%20who%20quit%20their%20W-2%20jobs%20to%20invest%20in%20real%20estate%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-investors-share-their-strategy-flip-and-buy-rentals-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epursue%20financial%20independence%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20do%20wholesales%2C%20wholetails%2C%20and%20flips%20primarily%20in%20Louisville.%20They%20also%20own%20more%20than%2020%20rental%20properties%2C%20including%20short-%2C%20mid-%2C%20and%20long-term%2C%20which%20BI%20verified%20by%20looking%20at%20settlement%20statements%20and%20closing%20documents.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGorius%20explained%20that%20there%20are%20three%20main%20ways%20to%20borrow%20money%20in%20their%20industry%3A%20through%20a%20private%20money%20lender%2C%20a%20hard%20money%20lender%2C%20or%20a%20traditional%20lender.%20Traditional%20lenders%20generally%20offer%20the%20lowest%20rates%2C%20while%20hard%20money%20lenders%20tend%20to%20be%20the%20most%20expensive.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BAs%20of%20right%20now%20having%20this%20conversation%2C%20what%20we%20are%20seeing%20is%20interest%20rates%20between%2010%25%20and%2012%25%20with%20private%20money%20lenders%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BHard%20money%20lenders%2C%20we're%20seeing%20between%2011%25%20and%2013%25%20%E2%80%94%20usually%20they're%20a%20little%20bit%20higher%20just%20because%20they're%20actually%20going%20to%20have%20some%20staff%20and%20office%20buildings%20%E2%80%94%20and%20if%20you%20went%20through%20Fannie%20Mae%20and%20Freddie%20Mac%2C%20interest%20rates%20are%206%25%20to%207%25%20right%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2250f2cc5b-471a-4864-b1a3-6f507f7ead4d%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EWorking%20with%20PMLs%20to%20close%20deals%20quickly%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20private%20lenders%20can't%20compete%20with%20traditional%20lenders%20on%20cost%2C%20they%20can%20offer%20speed%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that's%20important%20to%20Gorius%20and%20Hart%2C%20who%20are%20closing%20deals%20weekly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20our%20own%20inspections%20because%20Kevin%20has%20all%20the%20experience%20and%20we%20don't%20need%20to%20do%20an%20appraisal%20because%20we're%20working%20with%20off-market%20sellers%20who%20are%20happy%20to%20work%20with%20us%20on%20price%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gorius.%20%26quot%3BThings%20can%20just%20move%20a%20lot%20quicker.%20It's%20what%20allows%20us%20to%20buy%20properties%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20days%20versus%20a%20matter%20of%20weeks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGorius%20said%20the%20fastest%20they've%20ever%20closed%20on%20a%20deal%20was%20eight%20days%2C%20whereas%20working%20with%20a%20traditional%20lender%20would%20take%20at%20least%2030%20days%20and%20require%20more%20paperwork%20and%20headaches.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22mike%20gorius%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67dd8da263d72727e197e885%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGorius%20formed%20an%20official%20business%20partnership%20with%20Hart%20in%202024%20under%20the%20Joe%20Homebuyer%20franchise.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Mike%20Gorius%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20for%20executing%20the%20deal%2C%20there%20are%20a%20few%20parties%20in%20the%20room%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20all%20meet%20at%20the%20closing%20table%20virtually%20because%20these%20people%20are%20scattered%20across%20the%20US%2C%20so%20we%20have%20the%20seller%2C%20the%20title%20attorney%2C%20us%2C%20and%20essentially%20the%20bank%2C%20which%20is%20just%20a%20normal%20Joe%20Schmo%20that%20has%20capital.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGorius%20gives%20the%20example%20of%20a%20standard%20deal%20for%20him%20and%20Hart%20in%20Louisville%3A%20a%20flip%20that'll%20cost%20about%20%24150%2C000%20%E2%80%94%20%24100%2C000%20for%20the%20property%20and%20%2450%2C000%20for%20the%20renovations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThe%20private%20money%20lender%2C%20just%20like%20a%20bank%2C%20will%20deposit%20%24150%2C000%20into%20escrow.%20The%20%24100%2C000%20will%20go%20toward%20the%20seller%2C%20so%20they'll%20walk%20away%20having%20sold%20the%20house%2C%20and%20we%20will%20now%20be%20the%20owners%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20deed%20is%20in%20mine%20and%20Kevin's%20name%2C%20or%20our%20company%20name%2C%20and%20then%20the%20extra%20%2450%2C000%20is%20given%20to%20us%20at%20closing%2C%20so%20we%20now%20have%20%2450%2C000%20in%20our%20bank%20account%20that%20is%20to%20be%20used%20to%20rehab%20the%20house.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20terms%20vary%20depending%20on%20the%20comfort%20level%20of%20the%20lender.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BSome%20people%20want%20interest-only%20monthly%20payments%20to%20know%20that%20we%20still%20have%20some%20skin%20in%20the%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gorius.%20%26quot%3BOther%20folks%20are%20fine%20with%20having%20all%20the%20interest%20paid%20at%20the%20end.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnce%20the%20rehab%20is%20complete%20and%20Gorius%20and%20Hart%20are%20ready%20to%20sell%2C%20the%20new%20buyer%20will%20deposit%20the%20sales%20price%20into%20escrow%2C%20and%20the%20title%20attorney%20will%20ensure%20that%20the%20private%20money%20lender%20gets%20their%20initial%20%24150%2C000%20back%20plus%20interest.%20Gorius%20and%20Hart%20will%20collect%20the%20remaining%20amount%20in%20profit.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2298e86477-73b7-4a53-a887-337a3c76b389%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20find%20PMLs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFinding%20private%20money%20lenders%20typically%20requires%20networking%20and%20cold%20calling.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBefore%20Gorius%20built%20a%20network%20of%20lenders%2C%20he%20started%20with%20the%20900%20contacts%20in%20his%20phone.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20texted%20every%20single%20one%20of%20them%20and%20said%2C%20'Hey%2C%20I%20know%20we%20talked%20yesterday.'%20Or%2C%20'Hey%2C%20I%20know%20we%20haven't%20talked%20in%20years%2C%20but%20I'm%20now%20investing%20in%20real%20estate.%20I%20know%20that%20can%20be%20exciting%20for%20some%2C%20not%20exciting%20for%20others%2C%20but%20if%20you%20ever%20have%20any%20questions%