5%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20(not%20pictured)%20rents%20out%20her%20fields%20to%20dog%20owners.%3Cp%3ERawlstock%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMichaele%20Blakely%20was%20an%20organic%20farmer%20for%20more%20than%2040%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20lives%20on%2031%20acres%20in%20Washington%2C%20and%20rents%20her%20fields%20to%20dog%20owners.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20likes%20that%20it's%20a%20low-effort%20way%20to%20make%20money%20in%20retirement.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Michaele%20Blakely%2C%20who%20rents%20her%20land%20through%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sniffspot.com%2Flistings%2Fcarnation-wa%2Fgrowing-things-farm-1809%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3ESniffspot%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3E.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWorking%20as%20a%20self-employed%20organic%20farmer%2C%20I%20didn't%20have%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fretirement-planning%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eplan%20for%20retirement%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20My%20four%20kids%20wanted%20to%20pull%20out%20their%20hair%20in%20frustration%20with%20me.%20But%20I%20believed%20if%20you%20do%20the%20right%20thing%20and%20work%20hard%2C%20you'll%20generally%20be%20OK%20in%20this%20country.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI'm%2071%20now%2C%20and%20so%20far%2C%20that's%20been%20the%20case%20for%20me.%20I%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdont-work-full-time-fluidly-retired-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebecame%20semi-retired%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20right%20around%20the%20time%20the%20pandemic%20started%2C%20in%202020.%20Before%20then%20I%20was%20working%2012-14%20hour%20days%20raising%20poultry%2C%20cattle%2C%20pigs%2C%20and%20crops.%20In%20my%2060s%2C%20I%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20a%20few%20different%20autoimmune%20conditions%20that%20zapped%20my%20energy.%20I%20physically%20couldn't%20do%20the%20long%20days%20any%20more.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThen%2C%20I%20got%20long%20COVID%2C%20and%20needed%20to%20scale%20back%20even%20further.%20I%20kept%20a%20flock%20of%20goats%20and%20made%20goat-milk%20soap%20and%20botanical%20treatments%20and%20ointments.%20I%20ran%20a%20small%20vegetable%20stand%20on%20my%20property.%20Last%20year%2C%20I%20stopped%20doing%20that%2C%20too.%20These%20days%2C%20I'm%20officially%20retired%2C%20but%20I%20also%20have%20a%20unique%20side%20gig.%20I%20rent%20out%20my%20fields%20to%20dog%20owners%2C%20and%20it%20helps%20pad%20my%20income.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223754a705-2b59-4845-8729-ea7979358b87%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20rent%20out%20my%20fields%20for%20%2418%20an%20hour%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EToday%20I%20have%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrying-to-double-passive-income-strategies-2024-03%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethree%20streams%20of%20income%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20I%20rely%20heavily%20on%20social%20security%2C%20and%20I%20also%20took%20a%20reverse%20mortgage%20on%20my%20property.%20In%20addition%2C%20I%20make%20%24500%20to%20%241%2C500%20a%20month%20renting%20out%20my%20fields%20for%20people%20to%20walk%20and%20play%20with%20their%20dogs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20few%20years%20ago%20I%20noticed%20an%20ad%20on%20a%20local%20community%20Facebook%20group%2C%20looking%20for%20land%20owners%20who%20were%20interested%20in%20renting%20their%20land.%20I%20replied%2C%20and%20became%20one%20of%20the%20first%20hosts%20in%20Washington%20with%20a%20service%20called%20Sniffspot%2C%20which%20rents%20private%20dog%20par