3EThe%20first%20time%20I%20visited%20Four%20Seasons%20Koh%20Samui%20in%20September%202013%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20a%20movie%20star.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20worked%20at%20the%20old%20Four%20Seasons%20in%20Bangkok%20and%20was%20given%20a%20complimentary%20stay.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20joined%20the%20Four%20Seasons%20in%20Bangkok%20as%20a%20receptionist%20in%20October%202009.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20you%20arrive%20at%20the%20Four%20Seasons%20Koh%20Samui%20a%20bellman%20welcomes%20you%20by%20striking%20a%20Thai%20gong.%20You%20walk%20through%20the%20hotel's%20huge%20wooden%20doors%20to%20a%20panoramic%20view%20of%20the%20resort%20from%20the%20top%20of%20the%20hill.%20It's%20a%20dramatic%20arrival%20experience.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20my%20visit%20to%20Koh%20Samui%20in%202013%2C%20I%20saw%20my%20former%20line%20manager.%20He%20said%20the%20city%20hotel%20and%20resort%20had%20a%20different%20ambiance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Four%20Seasons%20Bangkok%20was%20popular%20with%20business%20people.%20They%20might%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BCan%20I%20have%20my%20room%20key%2C%20as%20I%20have%20a%20meeting%20in%2015%20minutes%3F%26quot%3B%20At%20Koi%20Samui%2C%20everyone%20comes%20here%20to%20relax%2C%20and%20no%20one%20is%20in%20a%20rush.%20There%20were%20more%20opportunities%20to%20connect%20with%20guests%20and%20make%20special%20touches%20for%20them%2C%20which%20appealed%20to%20me.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAround%20this%20time%2C%20the%20old%20Four%20Seasons%20Bangkok%20was%20rebranding%2C%20and%20opportunities%20became%20available%20at%20other%20Four%20Seasons.%20I%20talked%20with%20my%20manager%20and%20moved%20to%20Koh%20Samui.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ab0512c5-6e76-4ef5-bad3-231494a8a9e5%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EGolf%20carts%20and%20guest%20requests%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20March%202015%2C%20I%20became%20the%20guest%20ex