e%20island%20when%20a%20guest%20has%20lost%20their%20luggage.%20The%20only%20requests%20we%20will%20say%20no%20to%20are%20if%20they're%20illegal.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPerks%20do%20come%20with%20the%20job.%20I've%20enjoyed%20complimentary%20nights%20at%20other%20Four%20Seasons%20hotels%20in%20Singapore%20and%20Hong%20Kong.%20Because%20I%20need%20to%20know%20what%20to%20recommend%20to%20guests%2C%20I've%20enjoyed%20a%20cruise%20on%20the%20Four%20Seasons%20yacht%20and%20get%20to%20try%20new%20menus%20in%20the%20restaurant.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a7a4564b-7923-4240-80de-0d92238d2cca%5C%22%3EFilming%20The%20White%20Lotus%20at%20the%20Four%20Seasons%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20was%20the%20Director%20of%20Housekeeping%20when%20they%20filmed%20The%20White%20Lotus%20at%20our%20resort.%20The%20Four%20Seasons%20Koh%20Samui%20residences%20starred%20in%20The%20White%20Lotus%20as%20Ratliffe's%20room%2C%20the%20room%20of%20the%20three%20female%20friends%2C%20and%20Rick%20and%20Chelsea's%20room.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELooking%20after%20the%20cast%20and%20crew%20was%20a%20very%20different%20experience%20from%20looking%20after%20our%20regular%20guests.%20Our%20guests%20are%20here%20to%20relax%2C%20but%20the%20cast%20and%20crew%20were%20here%20to%20work.%20No%20one%20needed%20us%20to%20book%20a%20last-minute%20diving%20trip%20or%20a%20massage.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20were%20expecting%20a%20lot%20of%20paparazzi%20when%20filming%20started%2C%20but%20they%20kept%20the%20filming%20location%20such%20a%20secret%20that%20there%20weren't%20any%20issues.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20moment%20on%20the%20show%20that%20does%20happen%20in%20real%20life%20is%20when%20the%20character%20Belinda%20visits%20Thailand%20to%20learn%20Thai%20massage.%20Hotel%20staff%20members%20can%20go%20on%20secondment%20and%20work%20in%20other%20hotels%20to%20gain%20skills.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20couple%20of%20things%20that%20happened%20on%20the%20show%20wouldn't%20happen%20in%20real%20life.%20On%20the%20show%2C%20they've%20had%20people%20working%20in%20reception%20who%20were%20engaged%20and%20a%20security%20guard%20who%20wanted%20to%20date%20another%20employee.%20In%20real%20life%20there%20are%20regulations%20where%20a%20partner%20cannot%20be%20a%20direct%20report%2C%20or%20if%20you%20are%20a%20security%2C%20then%20you%20should%20not%20have%20your%20partner%20working%20in%20the%20hotel.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224b6a6363-716d-4bd3-b2e2-d596932798e5%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThai%20culture%20features%20on%20the%20show%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20enjoyed%20seeing%20the%20traditional%20Thai%20mural%20featured%20in%20the%20opening%20credits%20of%20each%20episode.%20It's%20a%20beautiful%20representation%20of%20our%20heritage.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20three%20female%20friends%20on%20the%20show%20experience%20the%20water%20festival%20Songkran%2C%20which%20takes%20place%20in%20April.%20This%20is%20a%20very%20auspicious%20time%20for%20us.%20The%20core%20part%20is%20to%20give%20thanks%20to%20your%20parents.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20the%20sprinkling%20of%20water%20would%20show%20reverence%2C%20respect%2C%20and%20good%20fortune%2C%20but%20somehow%20over%20time%2C%20the%20sprinkling%20of%20water%20has%20turned%20into%20a%20water%20fight.%20In%20the%20north%2C%20it's%20a%20three-day%20celebration%2C%20on%20Koh%20Samui%2C%20we%20celebrate%20it%20for%20the%20day.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20of%20our%20guests%20embrace%20Thai%20culture%20during%20their%20stay.%20They%20often%20greet%20us%20in%20Thai.%20We%20offer%20a%20complimentary%20Thai%20language%20class%20as%20part%20of%20our%20resort%20activities%20to%20allow%20guests%20to%20deepen%20their%20cultural%20connection.%20I%20appreciate%20how%20the%20show%20prominently%20features%20the%20Thai%20greeting%2C%20the%20'Wai'%2C%20when%20we%20press%20the%20palms%20of%20our%20hands%20together.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-work-four-seasons-thailand-white-lotus-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742637181000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ddb9a0b8b41a9673fb6853%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-work-four-seasons-thailand-white-lotus-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20White%20Lotus%20is%20filmed%20in%20part%20at%20the%20Four%20Seasons%20Koh%20Samui%20resort%20where%20Pimlalana%20Mankong%20works%20as%20a%20manager.%20She%20shares%20what%20the%20job%20is%20like.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Claire%20Turrell)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A122%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-work-four-seasons-thailand-white-lotus-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amid%20fair%20delimitation%20push%2C%20a%20%E2%80%98Sword%20of%20Damocles%E2%80%99%20warning%20from%20Kerala%20CM%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742636815000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-119338503%2Cimgsize-46276.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fchennai%2Fin-tamil-nadu-cm-mk-stalins-fair-delimitation-push-a-sword-of-damocles-warning-rings-loud-from-ally%2Farticleshow%2F119337450.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tamil%20Nadu's%20DMK-led%20Joint%20Action%20Committee%20meeting%2C%20chaired%20by%20CM%20M.K.%20Stalin%2C%20united%20multiple%20state%20leaders%20against%20population-based%20Lok%20Sabha%20delimitation.%20They%20argue%20this%20move%20threatens%20democratic%20representation%2C%20particularly%20for%20southern%20states%20that%20have%20successfully%20implemented%20population%20control%20measures.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20CITY%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canoni