ow%2F119337872.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20MK%20Stalin's%20Delimitation%20Push%2C%20A%20%26quot%3BSword%20Of%20Damocles%26quot%3B%20Warning%20From%20Ally%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin%20hosted%20the%20first%20meeting%20of%20the%20Joint%20Action%20Committee%20(JAC)%20on%20delimitation%20in%20Chennai%20today.%20The%20event%2C%20attended%20by%20leaders%20from%20multiple%20states%2C%20marked%20the%20beginning%20of%20what%20Mr%20Stalin%20described%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bnational%20movement%26quot%3B%20to%20ensure%20fair%20representation%20in%20Parliament.%20The%20meeting%20also%20drew%20criticism%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20accused%20the%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(DMK)%20of%20diverting%20attention%20from%20domestic%20governance%20issues%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20a%20political%20struggle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPush%20For%20%26quot%3BFair%20Delimitation%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20controversy%20lies%20the%20impending%20parliamentary%20seat%20delimitation%20exercise%2C%20which%20is%20expected%20to%20follow%20the%20next%20national%20census.%20According%20to%20current%20projections%2C%20southern%20states%20-%20including%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Kerala%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Telangana%20-%20stand%20to%20lose%20representation%20in%20Parliament%20due%20to%20their%20success%20in%20population%20control.%20In%20contrast%2C%20northern%20states%20with%20higher%20population%20growth%20could%20gain%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20JAC%20meeting%2C%20Mr%20Stalin%20said%20that%20the%20movement%20was%20not%20against%20delimitation%20itself%20but%20against%20an%20unfair%20implementation%20of%20it.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20against%20delimitation%3B%20we%20are%20for%20fair%20delimitation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20declared.%20He%20proposed%20forming%20a%20legal%20expert%20committee%20to%20chart%20out%20a%20comprehensive%20legal%20strategy%20to%20challenge%20the%20process%20if%20needed.%20%26quot%3BContinuous%20action%20is%20essential%20to%20establish%20our%20rights.%20Our%20representation%20must%20not%20decline%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20released%20a%20seven-point%20resolution%20on%20delimitation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAny%20delimitation%20exercise%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20Union%20Government%20to%20improve%20the%20content%20and%20character%20of%20democracy%20should%20be%20carried%20out%20transparently%2C%20enabling%20political%20parties%20of%20all%20the%20States%2C%20State%20Governments%20and%20other%20stakeholders%20to%20deliberate%2C%20discuss%20and%20contribute%20in%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20the%20resolutions%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20States%20which%20have%20effectively%20implemented%20the%20population%20control%20program%20and%20consequently%20whose%20population%20share%20has%20come%20down%2C%20should%20not%20be%20penalised.%20The%20Union%20Government%20must%20enact%20necessary%20constitutional%20amendments%20for%20this%20purpose.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPinarayi%20Vijayan's%20Warning%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKerala%20Chief%20Minister%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan%2C%20in%20his%20address%2C%20likened%20the%20delimitation%20proposal%20to%20the%20%26quot%3BSword%20of%20Damocles%26quot%3B%20hanging%20over%20the%20southern%20states.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3BSword%20of%20Damocles%26quot%3B%20is%20an%20ancient%20Roman%20moral%20parable%20about%20a%20king%20named%20Dionysius%20who%20wanted%20to%20show%20that%20power%20comes%20with%20constant%20anxiety.%20He%20let%20a%20man%20named%20Damocles%20sit%20in%20his%20place%20and%20enjoy%20the%20luxury%20of%20being%20king%20-%20but%20hung%20a%20sharp%20sword%20above%20his%20head%20by%20a%20single%20strand%20of%20horsehair.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D