strong%3Efull-time%20hours%20at%20Walt%20Disney%20World%20after%20the%20big%20stock%20market%20crash%20in%202008.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20getting%20scheduled%20for%20roughly%2070-hour%20weeks%20and%20at%20first%20that%20was%20fine.%20I%20was%20able%20to%20rent%20a%20room.%20But%20eventually%20Disney%20capped%20the%20number%20of%20hours%20you%20could%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20point%2C%20I%20could%20no%20longer%20pay%20rent.%20So%20I%20lived%20in%20my%202005%20Chevy%20Malibu%2C%20which%20I%20parked%20in%20West%20Clock%2C%20the%20Magic%20Kingdom%20cast%20member%20parking%20lot.%20I%20slept%20there%20and%20showered%20in%20the%20locker%20rooms%20every%20day%20for%20months%2C%20trying%20to%20get%20more%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ff81faff-ec75-4a03-9396-3e70fad27106%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20wasn't%20the%20only%20homeless%20cast%20member%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHonestly%2C%20there%20were%20so%20many%20people%20that%20slept%20in%20their%20cars%20in%20that%20parking%20lot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou're%20not%20supposed%20to%20sleep%20on%20the%20property%2C%20but%20the%20company%20turned%20a%20blind%20eye.%20When%20I%20was%20living%20in%20my%20car%2C%20I%20was%20one%20among%20dozens%20of%20others%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20not%20just%20me.%20Security%20knew%20we%20were%20doing%20this%2C%20and%20they%20knew%20we%20had%20nowhere%20else%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20was%20a%20theme%20park%20that%20put%20me%20in%20that%20situation%2C%20it%20was%20also%20a%20theme%20park%20that%20helped%20me%20get%20out%20of%20it.%20I%20got%20hired%20as%20an%20actor%20and%20dancer%20at%20Universal%20in%20November%202010.%20My%20first%20role%20there%20was%20for%20%26quot%3BGrinchmas%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20holiday%20event%20held%20at%20the%20theme%20park.%20Universal%20paid%20me%20%2415%20an%20hour%2C%20which%20together%20with%20my%20Disney%20hours%2C%20helped%20me%20finally%20rent%20an%20apartment%20with%20two%20other%20people%20and%20allowed%20me%20to%20afford%20basic%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22912%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jessica%20Cody%2C%20former%20Walt%20Disney%20World%20cast%20member%20and%20former%20Universal%20Orlando%20employee.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ddcb4763d72727e197f901%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22684%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJessica%20Cody.%3Cp%3EJessica%20Cody%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20never%20trade%20my%20time%20at%20Disney%20for%20anything.%20I%20learned%20more%20about%20the%20entertainment%20industry%20than%20I%20ever%20did%20in%20college%20or%20the%20audition%20circuit%20in%20New%20York%20City.%20I%20just%20think%20it%20is%20ridiculous%20that%20people%20have%20to%20choose%20between%20financial%20security%20and%20a%20job%20that%20fulfills%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20no%20longer%20work%20at%20Disney%20or%20Universal.%20At%20Disney%2C%20I%20went%20down%20to%20seasonal%2C%20and%20when%20you're%20seasonal%2C%20you%20have%20to%20work%20a%20certain%20amount%20of%20hours%20a%20year%20to%20keep%20your%20status.%20I%20just%20didn't%20work%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20Universal%2C%20I%20had%20my%20son%20around%20that%20time%20so%20I%20switched%20to%20a%20different%20department.%20I%20was%20in%20the%20call%20center%20for%20the%20last%20six%20months%20of%20my%20time%20at%20Universal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20now%20a%20dance%20teacher%20and%20choreographer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2237af8ac1-2208-41dc-8e2d-92d020db1ea6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECast%20members%20need%20livable%20wages%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDisney%20has%20made%20some%20positive%20changes%20in%20recent%20years%20with%20programs%20to%20help%20cast%20members.%20They%20also%20raised%20the%20minimum%20amount%20they%20pay%20people.%20But%2C%20in%20my%20opinion%2C%20it's%20still%20not%20a%20living%20wage%20as%20far%20as%20Orlando%20is%20concerned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20love%20Disney%20and%20still%20expect%20them%20to%20do%20better.%20There's%20no%20reason%20for%20any%20cast%20member%20to%20be%20on%20food%20stamps%20or%20unable%20to%20afford%20basic%20necessities.%20Until%20there%20are%20no%20cast%20members%20homeless%20or%20living%20on%20public%20assistance%2C%20we're%20not%20there%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20place%20would%20not%20be%20open%20if%20it%20weren't%20for%20the%20dedicated%20and%20amazing%20people%20working%20there%20who%20break%20their%20backs%20to%20bring%20joy%20to%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20are%20the%20people%20responsible%20for%20the%20theme%20park's%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEditor's%20note%3A%20Walt%20Disney%20World%20set%20a%20%2415%20minimum%20wage%20for%20cast%20members%20in%202021%20and%20increased%20it%20to%20%2418%20in%202023.%20The%20company%20offers%20employee%20packages%20with%20benefits.%20In%202022%2C%20Walt%20Disney%20World%20Resort%20announced%20it%20would%20develop%20affordable%20housing%20with%20over%201%2C000%20apartments%20available%20to%20cast%20members%20and%20the%20larger%20community%20in%20Orange%20County%2C%20Florida.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20working%20at%20Disney%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aledmonds%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Eledmonds%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalt-disney-world-cast-member-homeless-universal-florida-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742636102000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ddcbd069253ccddf9a06ac%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalt-disney-world-cast-member-homeless-universal-florida-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jessica%20Cody%20worked%20as%20a%20Walt%20Disney%20World%20cast%20member.%20Sh