g%20the%20state's%20progress.%20Mr%20Tharoor%20later%20backtracked%20on%20his%20praises%20after%20a%20report%20claimed%20over%2042%2C000%20MSMEs%20had%20shut%20down%20in%20Kerala%20over%20the%20past%20nine%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fa-shashi-tharoor-selfie-with-pinarayi-vijayan-days-after-congress-unity-show-7905750%5C%22%3EA%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20Selfie%20With%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan%20Days%20After%20Congress%20Unity%20Show%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20remark%20on%20a%20podcast%20-%20that%20he%20had%20other%20%26quot%3Boptions%26quot%3B%20if%20his%20service%20was%20not%20needed%20in%20the%20Congress%20-%20threatened%20to%20escalate%20the%20rift%2C%20but%20he%20swiftly%20clarified%20that%20he%20was%20not%20talking%20about%20political%20options%20but%20in%20the%20context%20of%20spending%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDays%20later%2C%20Mr%20Tharoor%20shared%20a%20selfie%20with%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan%2C%20who%20heads%20the%20Kerala%20LDF%20government%20and%20whose%20main%20political%20rival%20is%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20tried%20to%20project%20unity%20amid%20the%20rift%20buzz%20with%20its%20central%20leadership%20sharing%20videos%20with%20the%20senior%20leader.%20A%20post%20shared%20by%20former%20party%20chief%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20asserted%20that%20they%20%26quot%3Bstand%20as%20one%26quot%3B%20-%20with%20a%20photo%20of%20Mr%20Tharoor%20and%20other%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742629080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Ffg0d6q1g_shashi-tharoor-jay-panda_625x300_22_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-mp-baijayant-jay-pandas-finally-travelling-in-same-direction-selfie-with-shashi-tharoor-7982685%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20MP%20Shashi%20Tharoor's%20praises%20for%20his%20political%20rivals%20in%20Kerala%20had%20raised%20a%20storm%20within%20his%20