egend%20George%20Foreman%20dies%20at%2076%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742628452000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-119334122%2Cimgsize-47398.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fboxing-legend-george-foreman-dies-at-76%2Farticleshow%2F119334062.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F119334062.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EFormer%20heavyweight%20boxing%20champion%20George%20Foreman%20passed%20away%20at%20age%2076.%20Known%20for%20his%201968%20Olympic%20gold%20and%20world%20titles%20in%201973%20and%201994%2C%20Foreman%20was%20famous%20for%20his%20bouts%20with%20Joe%20Frazier%20and%20Muhammad%20Ali.%20Beyond%20boxing%2C%20he%20gained%20fame%20for%20his%20grilling%20machine.%20He%20left%20behind%20a%20legacy%20in%20sports%20and%20business.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fboxing-legend-george-foreman-dies-at-76%2Farticleshow%2F119334062.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fboxing-legend-george-foreman-dies-at-76%2Famp_articleshow%2F119334062.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fboxing-legend-george-foreman-dies-at-76%2Famp_articleshow%2F119334062.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bio-Farming%2C%20Muscle%20Loss%20To%20Be%20Among%20Indian%20Astronaut's%20Space%20Experiments%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian%20Air%20Force%20(IAF)%20Group%20Captain%20Shubhanshu%20Shukla%2C%20who%20is%20set%20to%20make%20history%20as%20the%20first%20Indian%20astronaut%20to%20travel%20to%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%20(ISS)%20this%20year%2C%20will%20likely%20conduct%20at%20least%20three%20experiments%2C%20including%20research%20on%20muscle%20loss%20in%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMinister%20of%20State%20(MoS)%20for%20Science%20and%20Technology%20Dr%20Jitendra%20Singh%20said%20Mr%20Shukla%20will%20focus%20on%20%26quot%3Bspace%20technology%2C%20space%20bio-manufacturing%20and%20bio-astronautics%26quot%3B%20during%20the%20latter's%20fortnight-long%20space%20mission.%20The%20IAF%20officer%20will%20grow%20special%20micro-organisms%20in%20the%20football-sized%20space%20station%20to%20look%20for%20edible%20algae%3B%20grow%20special%20bacteria%3B%20and%20study%20effect%20on%20muscle%20cells%2C%20and%20understand%20why%20astronauts%20face%20muscle%20loss%20in%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMedical%20experts%20have%20raised%20concerns%20over%20the%20health%20and%20muscle%20atrophy%20of%20Indian-origin%20astronaut%20Sunita%20Williams%2C%20who%20recently%20returned%20to%20Earth%20after%20a%20nine-month%20gruelling%20stay%20at%20the%20ISS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSpace%20is%20an%20unforgiving%20environment%20and%20just%20becoming%20an%20astronaut%20does%20not%20change%20the%20basic%20human%20physiology%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContinuous%20availability%20of%20nutrients%2C%20preservation%20of%20food%2C%20microgravity%2C%20radiation%2C%20physiological%20changes%20and%20health%20hazards%20in%20space%20travellers%2C%20potable%20water%20and%20a%20way%20to%20clean%20and%20use%20waste%20in%20a%20sustainable%20way%20are%20some%20of%20the%20key%20challenges%20in%20space%2C%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20has%20been%20projected%20that%20by%202050%2C%20commercial%20space%20travel%20is%20going%20to%20become%20a%20reality%20and%20we%20need%20to%20be%20future-ready.%20To%20this%20end%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Biotechnology%20(DBT)%20and%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organization%20(ISRO)%20will%20jointly%20take%20up%20mission%20projects%2C%20focusing%20on%20simple%20space%20bio-manufacturing%20demonstration%20experiments%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20National%20Aeronautics%20and%20Space%20Administration%20(NASA)%2C%20Mr%20Shukla%20will%20pilot%20the%20Axiom%20Mission%204%20(Ax-4)%2C%20a%20private%20astronaut%20mission%20launching%20aboard%20a%20SpaceX%20Dragon%20spacecraft.%20The%20American%20space%20agency%20is%20expected%20to%20launch%20the%20mission%20from%20the%20Kennedy%20Space%20Center%20in%20Florida%20possibly%20as%20early%20as%20May.%20The%20crew%20will%20conduct%20experiments%2C%20outreach%20programs%20and%20commercial%20activities%20in%20microgravity%20as%20part%20of%20a%20collaboration%20between%20NASA%20and%20ISRO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fjep2lu0c_muscle-loss-research_625x300_22_March_25.jpeg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20third%20experiment%20will%20focus%20on%20the%20adverse%20effects%20of%20space%20conditions%20on%20the%20physiology%20of%20astronauts.%20(DBT)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20said%20the%20micro-gravity%20environment%20will%20offer%20unique%20challenges.%20The%20Indian%20experiments%2C%20however%2C%20will%20aid%20the%20upcoming%20Gaganyaan%20and%20Bhartiya%20Antariksh%20Station%20programs%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProviding%20details%2C%20the%20MoS%20said%20the%20first%20experiment%20will%20involve%20using%20some%20edible%20microalgae%20to%20grow%20them%20in%20space%20and%20see%20if%20they%20are%20found%20resilient%20in%20space%20conditions%20and%20can%20serve%20as%20a%20sustainable%20source%20of%20food%20like%20protein%2C%20carbohydrate%2C%20lipids%20and%20Vitamins%20A%2C%20B1%2C%20B2%2C%20B6%2C%20B12%2C%20C%20and%20E%20for%20astronauts%20during%20extended%20space%20expeditions.%20These%20algae%20will%20be%20grown%20in%20enclosed%20containers%20and%20will%20be%20fed%20with%20water%20and%20carbon%20dioxide%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20experiment%20will%20be%20spearheaded%20by%20the%20International%20Center%20for%20Genetic%20Engineering%20and%20Biotechnology%20(ICGEB)%2C%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20experiment%2C%20also%20led%20by%20the%20ICGEB%2C%20will%20aim%20for%20waste-to-wealth%20creation%20in%20space.%20The%20urea%20present%20in%20the%20urine%20of%20the%20astronauts%20will%20be%20used%20to%20grow%20some%20blue-green%20algae%20named%20spirulina%20and%20a%20desert%20species%20called%20Chroococcidiopsis%2C%20the%20minister%20says.%20Resource%20recycling%20is%20critical%20in%20space%20as%20hauling%20material%20is%20extremely%20costly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20says%20the%20third%20experiment%20will%20be%20headed%20by%20the%20Institute%20for%20Stem%20Cell%20Science%20and%20Regenerative%20Medicine%20(INSTEM)%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20and%20will%20focus%20on%20the%20adverse%20effects%20of%20space%20conditions%20on%20the%20physiology%20of%20astronauts%2C%20and%20how%20to%20mitigate%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20suggest%20that%20astronauts%20experience%20up%20to%2020%25%20muscle%20loss%20in%20space%20flights%20lasting%20five%20to%2011%20days.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20muscle%20loss%20or%20Sarcopenia%20takes%20decades%20to%20develop%20on%20Earth.%20By%20using%20supplements%20in%20a%20muscle%20cell%20culture%20model%2C%20researchers%20are%20attempting%20to%20increase%20mitochondrial%20function%2C%20which%20is%20an%20important%20component%20in%20this%20condition.%20On%20Earth%2C%20this%20experiment%20is%20expected%20to%20help%20patients%20face%20similar%20muscle%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20bio-economy%20has%20experienced%20remarkable%20growth%20-%20from%20%2410%20billion%20in%202014%20to%20over%20%24151%20billion%20in%202023%2C%20with%20projections%20to%20reach%20%24300%20billion%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20DBT%20said%20the%20collaboration%20with%20ISRO%20will%20advance%20space%20biotechnology%20research%20in%20India%20and%20contribute%20significantly%20to%20the%20space%20economy%20of%20our%20country.%20The%20space%20economy%20is%20expected%20to%20grow%20five%20times%20in%20the%20next%2010%20years%2C%20to%20around%20%2444%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20niche%20areas%20is%20space%20bio-manufacturing%2C%20which%20has%20immense%20commercial%20potential%20like%20%26quot%3Bartificial%20organ%20development%26quot%3B%20that%20requires%20scaffolding%20on%20Earth%20to%20keep%20the%20tissue%20layers%20together.%20When%20experiments%20are%20conducted%20in%20space%2C%20the%20tissue%20layers%20do%20not%20fall%20apart%20and%20scaffolding%20is%20not%20required.%20DBT%20and%20ISRO%20will%20also%20look%20into%20organoids%20development%20in%20space%2C%20with%20a%20future%20goal%20of%20artificial%20organ%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20be%20noted%20that%20three%20very%20simple%20experiments%20to%20grow%20Lobia%20seed%2C%20bacteria%20and%20aggregates%20of%20spinach%20cells%20in%20space%20were%20done%20on%20an%20ISRO%20module%20called%20POEM%20earlier%20this%20year.%20These%20were%20the%20first%20biology-related%20experiments%20done%20by%20Indians%20in%20the%20microgravity%20of%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742628000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Frit0v8hs_algae-research_625x300_22_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fndtv-exclusive-the-experiments-indian-astronaut-will-conduct-in-space-7979625%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20Air%20Force%20Group%20Captain%20Shubhanshu%20Shukla%2C%20who%20is%20set%20to%20make%20history%20as%20the%20first%20Indian%20astronaut%20to%20travel%20to%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%2C%20will%20likely%20conduct%20at%20least%20three%20experiments%2C%20including%20research%20on%20muscle%20loss%20in%20space.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22