aders%20from%20at%20least%20five%20states%20and%20they%20would%20deliberate%20on%20the%20'threat'%20posed%20by%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20delimitation%20exercise%20to%20states%20with%20high%20economic%20growth%20and%20literacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20BJP%2C%20which%20staged%20a%20black%20flag%20protest%2C%20slammed%20Stalin%20for%20not%20convening%20similar%20meetings%20on%20the%20Cauvery%20and%20Mullaiperiar%20water-sharing%20disputes%20with%20Karnataka%20and%20Kerala%2C%20respectively.%20BJP%20leader%20Tamilisai%20Soundararajan%20described%20the%20meeting%20as%20%26quot%3Bcorruption%20hiding%20meeting%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20respective%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20Deputy%20CM%20DK%20Shivakumar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bat%20any%20cost%2C%20we%20cannot%20let%20down%20our%20country%20and%20our%20seats%20to%20be%20reduced.%26quot%3B%20He%20claimed%20South%20India%20had%20always%20upheld%20the%20census%20regulations%20and%20family%20planning%20policies%2C%20making%20it%20a%20progressive%20region.%20%26quot%3BEconomically%20and%20in%20terms%20of%20literacy%2C%20we%20have%20consistently%20led%20the%20way.%20We%20have%20always%20protected%20the%20national%20interest%2C%20not%20just%20our%20own%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20upon%20his%20arrival%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20national%20spokesperson%20C%20R%20Kesavan%20said%20on%20the%20meeting%20that%20the%20DMK%20was%20staging%20the%20delimitation%20drama%20%26quot%3Bas%20a%20divisionary%20tactic%20to%20deflect%20public%20attention%20away%20from%20DMK's%20corrupt%2C%20failed%2C%20disastrous%20misrule.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDMK's%20divisive%20politics%20of%20fear%20mongering%2C%20attempting%20to%20mislead%20and%20misinform%20people%20will%20badly%20boomerang%20back%20on%20the%20DMK.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Congress%2C%20with%20their%20mutually%20conflicting%20and%20contradicting%20stand%20on%20delimitation%2C%20are%20indulging%20in%20a%20very%20pathetic%20politics%20of%20opportunism%20which%20is%20utterly%20condemnable%2C%26quot%3B%20Kesavan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Telangana%20Governor%20and%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20Tamilisai%20Soundararajan%20said%20the%20black%20flag%20protest%20was%20to%20safeguard%20the%20interests%20of%20people%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20asked%20Stalin%20if%20he%20held%20any%20meetings%20to%20solve%20the%20Cauvery%20problem%20and%20Mullaperiyar%20dam%20issue%20with%20the%20Karnataka%20and%20Kerala%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20delimitation%20has%20not%20been%20announced%2C%20and%20not%20a%20single%20word%20has%20been%20uttered%20by%20the%20central%20government...Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20came%20to%20Coimbatore.%20He%20had%20clarified%20that%20Tamil%20Nadu%20will%20not%20be%20affected.%20The%20Home%20Minister%20has%20clarified%20it%2C%20so%20on%20what%20basis%20are%20you%20conducting%20this%20meeting%2C%26quot%3B%20She%20asked%20the%20ruling%20DMK%20chief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20meeting%20was%20being%20held%20%26quot%3Bto%20hide%20the%20corruption%20charges%2C%20to%20divide%20the%20people%20of%20the%20country.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThe%20concerned%20CMs%20who%20are%20attending%20the%20meeting%20are%20doing%20so%20to%20hide%20the%20misgoverance%20in%20the%20concerned%20states.%20There%20are%20so%20many%20corruption%20charges%20in%20Telangana%2C%20Kerala.%20Their%20own%20people%20will%20be%20against%20their%20CMs%20attending%20this%20event%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20claimed%20while%20speaking%20to%20PTI%20Videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstead%20of%20calling%20this%20a%20delimitation%20meeting%2C%20it%20can%20be%20called%20corruption%20hiding%20meeting%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Chief%20Ministers%20of%20Kerala%2C%20Telangana%2C%20and%20Punjab--Pinarayi%20Vijayan%2C%20Revanth%20Reddy%2C%20Bhagwant%20Singh%20Mann%2C%20and%20working%20president%20of%20Shiromani%20Akali%20Dal%20Balwinder%20Singh%20Bhunder%2C%20and%20general%20secretary%20of%20Indian%20Union%20Muslim%20League%20Kerala%20P%20M%20A%20Salam%2C%20were%20among%20the%20leaders%20who%20had%20arrived%20in%20Chennai%20to%20take%20part%20in%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKerala%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Telangana%2C%20Odisha%2C%20West%20Bengal%20and%20Punjab%20are%20the%20seven%20states%20the%20DMK%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20for%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20historic%20day%20for%20Indian%20federalism%2C!%26quot%3B%20Stalin%20had%20said%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribing%20the%20DMK-led%20all-party%20meeting%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Blandmark%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20which%20as%20many%20as%2058%20parties%20participated%20by%20putting%20aside%20difference%20for%20a%20single%20cause%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bthis%20overwhelming%20consensus%20reflected%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20unwavering%20commitment%26quot%3B%20to%20democracy%20and%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20CM%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BBuilding%20on%20this%20historic%20unity%2C%20our%20MPs%20and%20Ministers%20actively%20engaged%20with%20leaders%20from%20other%20affected%20states%2C%20strengthening%20our%20collective%20resolve.%20What%20started%20as%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20initiative%20has%20now%20grown%20into%20a%20national%20movement%2C%20with%20states%20across%20India%20joining%20hands%20to%20demand%20fair%20representation.%20This%20is%20a%20defining%20moment%20in%20our%20collective%20journey.%20This%20is%20more%20than%20a%20meeting-it%20is%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20movement%20that%20will%20shape%20the%20future%20of%20our%20country.%20Together%2C%20we%20will%20achieve%20%23FairDelimitation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742626920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Frung