year%2C%20compared%20to%20nearly%20%24111%20million%20the%20British%20Royal%20Family%20received%20in%20the%20last%20three%20years.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20money%20is%20used%20to%20cover%20staff%20expenditures%20and%20any%20costs%20associated%20with%20their%20official%20responsibilities%2C%20such%20as%20travel.%20The%20Grand%20Duke%20has%20an%20excellent%20real%20estate%20portfolio%2C%20unique%20jewels%2C%20acres%20of%20land%2C%20and%20private%20holdings%20--%20all%20contributing%20to%20his%20%244%20billion%20net%20worth.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHe%20has%20an%20extraordinary%20collection%20of%20jewels%20and%20a%20sizable%20estate.%20Duke%20Henri%20%E2%80%94%20the%20first%20cousin%20of%20Prince%20Robert%20of%20Luxembourg%20%E2%80%94%20owns%20three%20official%20properties%3A%20Fischbach%20Castle%2C%20Berg%20Castle%2C%20and%20the%20Grand%20Ducal%20Palace.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20Grand%20Ducal%20Palace%20is%20not%20the%20Duke's%20primary%20residence%2C%20it%20is%20his%20formal%20residence.%20Located%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20Luxembourg%20City%2C%20the%20Ducal%20Palace%20is%20accessible%20to%20visitors%20during%20the%20summer.%20Berg%20Castle%20in%20Colmar-Berg%20is%20the%20primary%20residence%20of%20Duke%20Henri.%20The%20gardens%20of%20Berg%20Castle%20are%20available%20to%20visitors%20on%20June%2023%2C%20Luxembourg's%20National%20Day%2C%20every%20year.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnFischbach%20Castle%20served%20as%20Duke%20Henri's%20primary%20residence%20during%20his%20tenure%20as%20the%20heir%20apparent%2C%20before%20he%20officially%20left%20in%202000.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnDuke%20Henri%20caused%20a%20nationwide%20uproar%20in%202006%20when%2C%20a%20year%20after%20his%20mother%2C%20Grand%20Duchess%20Jos%C3%A9phine-Charlotte's%20death%2C%C2%A0he%20put%20some%20of%20her%C2%A0diamonds%20up%20for%20auction.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnSoon%20after%2C%20the%20monarch%20came%20under%20fire%20from%20the%20public%2C%20who%20claimed%20he%20was%20selling%20pieces%20of%20the%20country's%20%26quot%3Bnational%20heritage%26quot%3B%20for%20extra%C2%A0money.%20Duke%20Henri%20consequently%20withdrew%20his%20late%20mother's%20belongings%20from%20the%20auction.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnSpeaking%20of%20the%20British%20Royal%20Family%2C%20while%20King%20Charles%20and%20Queen%20Camilla's%20net%20worth%20stands%20at%20%24780%20million%2C%20Prince%20William%20and%20Kate%20Middleton%20are%20thought%20to%20be%20worth%20approximately%20%241.3%20billion%20as%20a%20result%20of%20his%20rich%20inheritance%20from%20the%20estate%20of%20the%20Duchy%20of%20Cornwall.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742625840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F1belopr8_duke-henri-of-luxembourg_625x300_22_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmeet-grand-duke-henri-richest-european-royal-from-luxembourg-with-4-billion-net-worth-7981882%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Monarchs%20no%20longer%20have%20ultimate%20power%20but%20many%20of%20them%20are%20still%20extremely%20wealthy.%20And%20some%20royal%20families%20are%20wealthier%20than%20we%20might%20imagine.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20monarch%20of%20Luxembourg%2C%20Grand%20Duke%20Henri%2C%20has%20an%20incredible%20net%20worth%20of%20%244%20billion.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmeet-grand-duke-henri-richest-european-royal-from-luxembourg-with-4-billion-net-worth-7981882%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Migrant%20deaths%20reach%20record%20high%20in%202024%2C%20IOM%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742625570000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-119332817%2Cimgsize-130164.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fmigrant-deaths-reach-record-high-in-2024-iom-says%2Farticleshow%2F119332791.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20