aw%20Rishi%20Sunak%20might%20have%20served%20as%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20but%20that%20made%20no%20difference%20to%20their%20equation%2C%20the%20author-philanthropist%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhether%20he%20is%20the%20prime%20minister%20or%20not%2C%20he%20is%20our%20son-in-law%2C%20we%20love%20him%20the%20same%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Murty%20said%20on%20NDTV's%20'India%20Through%20the%20Eyes%20of%20Its%20Icons'%20show.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnShe%20also%20quoted%20the%20third%20daughter%20from%20Shakespeare's%20iconic%20play%20King%20Lear.%20%26quot%3BAs%20the%20third%20daughter%20in%20King%20Lear%20said%3A%20'I%20love%20my%20father%20as%20much%20as%20a%20daughter%20should%20love%20a%20father'.%20Similarly%2C%20whatever%20may%20be%20Rishi's%20position%2C%20I%20love%20him%20like%20a%20new%20son.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BIn%20no%20way%20it%20has%20affected%20us%3B%20it%20would%20have%20been%20the%20same%20if%20he%20lived%20in%20the%20same%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Murty%20added.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnWhile%20nothing%20changed%20between%20Sudha%20Murty%C2%A0and%20Rishi%20Sunak%2C%20she%20agreed%20that%20the%20world%20started%20looking%20at%20her%20differently%20after%20he%20became%20the%20British%20Prime%20Minister.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20money%2C%20people%20view%20you%20in%20a%20different%20way%3B%20new%20friendships%20will%20come%2C%20new%20acquaintances%20will%20come%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20people's%20expectations%20of%20you%20also%20change.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BWhen%20Rishi%2C%20our%20son-in-law%20became%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20people%20started%20asking%20me%20for%20a%20lot%20of%20favours%20in%20England%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Murty%20said.%20But%20she%20told%20them%20he%20was%20the%20PM%20of%20another%20country%20and%20she%20couldn't%20ask%20for%20any%20favours.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BPeople%20started