erformed%20the%20last%20rites%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20men%20-%20Imran%2C%20Shahrukh%2C%20Sonu%2C%20Ejaz%20-%20were%20arrested%20for%20the%20'murder'.%20The%20suspects%2C%20who%20are%20in%20jail%20pending%20a%20trial%2C%20have%20now%20filed%20a%20petition%20in%20the%20local%20court%20citing%20the%20woman's%20reappearance.%20The%20court%20has%20sought%20information%20about%20the%20matter%2C%20said%20Jhabua%20Superintendent%20Police%20(SP)%20Padmavilochan%20Shukla.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20first%20conduct%20a%20medical%20examination%20and%20DNA%20test%20of%20the%20woman%2C%20and%20also%20record%20afresh%20the%20statements%20of%20witnesses.%20Only%20after%20a%20thorough%20investigation%2C%20we%20would%20be%20able%20to%20state%20conclusively%20that%20the%20woman%20who%20turned%20up%20at%20Gandhi%20Sagar%20police%20station%20earlier%20this%20month%20is%20the%20same%20woman%20who%20was%20thought%20to%20have%20been%20murdered%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shukla%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742622000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fms3e1708_lalita-bai_625x300_22_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fcities%2Fmadhya-pradesh-mandsaur-woman-presumed-dead-returns-home-father-had-identified-body-with-crushed-head-and-cremated-7982106%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20an%20incident%20stranger%20than%20a%20movie%20script%2C%20a%2035-year-old%20woman%20believed%20to%20have%20been%20murdered%20in%202023%20has%20returned%20home%2C%20leaving%20his%20family%20and%20friends%20surprised.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fcities%2Fmadhya-pradesh-mandsaur-woman-presumed-dead-returns-home-father-had-identified-body-with-crushed-head-and-cremated-7982106%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tamil%20Cinema%20stars%20who%20are%20engineers%22%2