a-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERespite%20came%20in%20the%20form%20of%20help%20from%20herpetologist%20Romulus%20Whitaker%2C%20who%20aided%20the%20establishment%20of%20the%20Irula%20Snake%20Catchers%20Industrial%20Cooperative%20Society%20(ISCICS)%20in%201978.%20The%20cooperative%20has%20risen%20to%20the%20ranks%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20largest%20producer%20of%20snake%20venom.%20But%20venom%20collection%20is%20just%20a%20part%20of%20the%20collective%E2%80%99s%20overarching%20aim%20of%20sustainable%20employment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajendra%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Irula%20tribe%2C%20elaborated%20on%20the%20process%20of%20venom%20tapping.%C2%A0%20Once%20tracked%20down%2C%20the%20venomous%20snakes%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F12062%2Fmeet-snake-man-of-india-vava-suresh-thiruvananthapuram%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethink%20cobras%2C%20kraits%2C%20Russell%E2%80%99s%20vipers%20and%20saw-scaled%20vipers%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20are%20settled%20into%20clay%20pots%20that%20are%20half-filled%20with%20sand.%20Each%20pot%20houses%20two%20snakes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2Fsnake-collective-1742466613.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20clay%20pots%20house%20the%20venomous%20snakes%20from%20whom%20venom%20is%20collected.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2Fsnake-collective-1742466613.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2Fsnake-collective-1742466613-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads