0Because%20they%20bring%20a%20unique%20and%20personal%20lens%20to%20the%20story.%20Roundglass%20Sustain%2C%20she%20points%20out%2C%20is%20simply%20visibilising%20these%20powerful%20narratives.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20impact%20storytellers%2C%20the%20team%20at%20Roundglass%20Sustain%20partners%20and%20collaborates%20with%20women%20who%20are%20scientists%20and%20researchers%2C%20writers%2C%20journalists%2C%20filmmakers%2C%20photographers%2C%20and%20illustrators%2C%20and%20provides%20them%20with%20a%20platform%20to%20amplify%20their%20narratives%20and%20tell%20their%20stories%20in%20their%20voice.%20Over%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20Roundglass%20Sustain%20has%20partnered%20with%20more%20than%20200%20women%20creators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20In%20Search%20of%20Kasturi%3A%20Capturing%20the%20story%20of%20the%20musk%20deer%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeha%E2%80%99s%20feet%20ached%20as%20she%20crouched%20behind%20a%20snow-covered%20bush%20in%20the%20Himalayan%20highlands%2C%20awaiting%20the%20musk%20deer.%20But%2C%20neither%20the%20sub-zero%20temperatures%20nor%20the%20treacherous%20terrain%20could%20deter%20her.%20She%20was%20there%20with%20a%20rock-solid%20mission.%20She%20wanted%20to%20capture%20the%20musk%20deer%20on%20camera.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20went%20in%20aware%20that%20even%20people%20who%E2%80%99ve%20lived%20there%20for%20decades%20have%20not%20seen%20the%20animal.%20It%20being%20crepuscular%20(active%20in%20twilight)%20means%20a%20limited%20number%20of%20hours%20in%20which%20it%20can%20be%20spotted.%20And%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F390643%2Fhow-to